# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok percy yutar , the prosecutor who won life sentences against nelson mandela and other african national congress leaders in the #### <unk> trial , has died .
# ::alignments
(d / die-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Percy"
                  :op2 "Yutar")
            :ARG0-of (p2 / prosecute-01)
            :ARG0-of (w / win-01
                  :ARG1 (s / sentence-01
                        :ARG1 (a / and
                              :op1 (p3 / person
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Nelson"
                                          :op2 "Mandela"))
                              :op2 (p4 / person
                                    :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                                          :ARG1 (g / government-organization
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "National"
                                                      :op2 "Congress")
                                                :mod (c / continent
                                                      :name (n4 / name
                                                            :op1 "Africa"))))
                                    :mod (o / other)))
                        :ARG2 (l2 / life)
                        :subevent-of (t / try-02
                              :ARG1 a)))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the bush administration cautiously welcomed an effort by former president clinton to help resolve the crisis in northern ireland and said president bush had offered to be helpful as well .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (w / welcome-01
            :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                  :ARG0-of (a2 / administrate-01)
                  :mod (p / person
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Bush")))
            :ARG1 (e / effort-01
                  :ARG0 (p2 / person
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Clinton")
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG2 (p3 / president)
                              :time (f / former)))
                  :ARG1 (h2 / help-01
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG1 (r / resolve-01
                              :ARG0 p2
                              :ARG1 (c / crisis
                                    :location (c2 / country-region
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Northern"
                                                :op2 "Ireland"))))))
            :manner (c3 / cautious))
      :op2 (s / say-01
            :ARG0 g
            :ARG1 (o / offer-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (h3 / helpful-04
                        :ARG0 p)
                  :mod (a3 / as-well))))

                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "U.S.")))
                        :ARG2 (o / official
                              :mod (t / top))))
            :purpose (c3 / coordinate-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (h3 / help-01
                        :ARG1 (m3 / medicine)
                        :ARG2 (h4 / haiti

                                    :ARG0 (q / quake-01)))

                                                      :quant 1
                                                      :unit (y / year))))))))

                                          :name (n / name
                                                :op1 "Toyota")))

                                    :polarity -))
                        :ARG1 (d / die-01
                              :ARG1 (p / person)))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (m / monday)))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :time (b / burglarize-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :location (h2 / here)
                        :time (e2 / early
                              :op1 (d / date-entity
                                    :weekday (m2 / monday))))))
      :ARG2 (s2 / suspect-01
            :ARG1 m
            :ARG2 (s3 / string
                  :consist-of (d2 / die-01
                        :quant 5
                        :ARG1-of (s4 / shoot-02)
                        :location (s5 / south
                              :part-of (s6 / state
                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "Carolina")))
                        :time (b2 / before
                              :op1 (n2 / now)
                              :duration (m3 / multiple
                                    :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                                          :quant 1
                                          :unit (d3 / day))))))))

                                    :mod (p2 / police))

      :ARG0 (c / country
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Iran")
            :ARG0-of (d / defy-01
                  :ARG1 (w / warn-01
                        :ARG0 (p / person
                              :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                                    :ARG1 (o / organization
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "European"
                                                :op2 "Union")))))))
      :ARG1 (r / remove-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (s2 / seal
                  :ARG1-of (p2 / place-01
                        :ARG0 (a / agency
                              :mod (n3 / nucleus)
                              :mod o))
                  :ARG2 (s3 / site
                        :quant 1
                        :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                              :ARG2 (s4 / site
                                    :mod (n4 / nucleus)
                                    :poss c))))
            :purpose (r2 / restart-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (a2 / activity-06
                        :location s4)))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (m / monday)))
